                <h1>Do Background Checks Include GPA? Understand What Employers See</h1>
                <p>Background checks typically focus on criminal records, employment history, and education verification. While some employers may request educational details like your degree, not all checks include GPA. If GPA is crucial for the job, employers often ask directly, as it may not be part of standard background check reports.</p>
